title: Watch What Happened When Westboro Baptist Messed With The Wrong Group Of Students
text: A crowd of high school students drove Westboro Baptist Church protestors away from their school in Kansas City, Missouri last week where the hate group gathered to protest the recent election of a transgender girl as homecoming queen.
